  "@id": "https://bio.tools/antibody-antigen_docking_service",
  "@type": "sc:SoftwareApplication",
  "dcterms:conformsTo": "https://bioschemas.org/profiles/ComputationalTool/0.6-DRAFT",
  "sc:description": "The Antibody-Antigen Docking Service is a crucial tool in modern biomedical research. It allows for in-depth exploration of how antibodies bind to their specific antigens, which is fundamental for understanding immune responses and developing new treatments. CD ComputaBio's docking service is designed to aid researchers in their quest to develop more efficient and effective therapeutics.",
